	02  DD-MM	PIC XX.
	02  FILLER	PIC X VALUE '/'.
	02  DD-DD	PIC XX.
	02  FILLER	PIC X VALUE '/'.
	02  DD-YY	PIC XX.


01  SUB		PIC S9(10) COMP.
01  DELIM-SPACE 	PIC X VALUE SPACE.
